Note 005 (part number 340017-01). Austin, TX: National Instruments
Corporation, 1991.
<P>
Powell, Robert L., George W. Burns et al. <I>Thermocouple Reference
Tables Based on the IPTS68</I>. NBS Monograph 125. Washington,
D.C.: U.S. Department of Commerce, 1974. 
