<BODY>
<H1>Hello</H1><BR>
 <BR>
<H3><STRONG>Under Construction</H3>
But since Kathrin is too slack to do anything about it, I will.

Kathrin is from Germany which is on the other side of the planet.
Germany is famous for beer (a good thing) and men in short, tight
leather pants (a not so good thing).  Kathrin's boyfriend (also a Geman national) likes playing
with rocks (a not so good thing for Kathrin), fortunately they are
volcanic most of the time and Kathrin is allowed to play with them
too.<BR>
<BR>
Kathrin sings in a beautiful choir which charges people to go and see them, and
listen too, so they must be good.<BR>
<BR>
Kathrin is German for Kathrine, while Winklemann means "to wink at men
in a seductive manner hinting at possible future liasons".<BR>
<BR>

