<H1>Exercise GE1 (cont.): STEEL BRACKET<P>
A multi-feature part</H1>

<!-- next filename.gif should have same stem as present filename.html -->
<IMG SRC="bracket.gif">
<HR>
<!-- next nextfile.html must match next file in series -->
<A HREF="lego_person.html"><IMG SRC="skip.gif"></A><P>

<H2><A NAME="start">Contents (`STEEL BRACKET'):</A></H2>
<OL>
<LI><A HREF="#oview">OVERVIEW OF THIS PART</A>
<LI><A HREF="#datums">DATUM PLANES (the first feature)</A>
<LI><A HREF="#feat_angle">EXTRUDED ANGLE SECTION</A>
<LI><A HREF="#saving">SAVING YOUR WORK</A>
<LI><A HREF="#feat_rounds">ROUNDED EDGES</A>
<LI><A HREF="#feat_slot_hole">A SLOT AND A HOLE</A>
