<HR>
<H3><A NAME="started">GETTING STARTED:</A></H3>

Before you begin this new part, ensure that you have saved any previous work
in the current Pro/ENGINEER session (by selecting <B>Dbms -&gt; Save</B>
from the MAIN menu, and typing a <B>&lt;CR&gt;</B> to accept the proposed
name).  This might also be a good time to get rid of all the out-dated 
versions of the part you have just finished, so that disk space is not wasted.  
If that part is still current, just select <B>Dbms -&gt; Purge</B> from the
MAIN menu, and type a <B>&lt;CR&gt;</B> to accept the default.  The
<B>Purge</B> command is quite safe -- it leaves you with only the latest
version of your part file.<P>

If the previous part you were working on is to be submitted for
