<P><KBD>Enter Part name [PRT0001]: <B>leg_l &lt;CR&gt;</B></KBD><P>

<!------------------------------------------------------------------------->
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="oview">OVERVIEW OF THIS PART (the leg_l):</A></H3>

Note that the left leg is a mirror image of the right leg.  We will therefore
take a short-cut in creating this second leg.  These instructions assume that
you have modelled the right leg first.

<P><A HREF="#start">Return to Contents at the start of this document ? <IMG ALIGN=top SRC="back.gif"></A>

<!------------------------------------------------------------------------->
<HR>
