There are many ways to model the `leg_l' part.  One suggested approach is
to use the following steps to derive the left leg's features from those
of the right:
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#copy_part">Start with a copy of the first leg</A>
<LI><A HREF="#mirrored_copy">Mirror-copy all features (Independent)</A>
<LI><A HREF="#delete_original">Delete the original feature</A>
</UL>

