<H1>Exercise GE1 (cont.): ... LEGO(tm) RIGHT LEG</H1>

<!-- next filename.gif should have same stem as present filename.html -->
<IMG SRC="leg_r_A.gif"><IMG SRC="leg_r_B.gif"><IMG SRC="leg_r_C.gif">
