<A HREF="http://hakatai.mcli.dist.maricopa.edu/tut/tut2.html">next:  "Modifying HTML"</A> |
</h5>
<p>
<HR>
<b>Writing HTML</b> Lesson 1: Creating Your First HTML Document<br>
