<h1 align=center><font SIZE=+4>UCant Dance</font></h1>

<h2 align=center>(formerly The Latin Dance Club of Canterbury University)</h2>

<p>UCant Dance exists to promote social dance at Canterbury University
and Christchurch. We hold dance classes and organise regular social events.
The club welcomes non-student members. 
<br>
<br>Formerly the Latin Dance Club, UCant Dance teaches a number of different
styles of social dance. NOT Folk dance, NOT Ballroom, NOT Ballet or Jazz
dance, we teach moves you can use at a nightclub or party-yes-with a partner-yes
you. Dances include Freestyle (club music), Latin Merengue and Salsa, and
possibly Rock'n'Roll and Tango. 
<br>The dances are easy, fast, flashy, and fun. </p>

<h2>
<br>Class Times d<b><font SIZE=+2>uring 1997, beginning Monday March 10.</font></b></h2>

<p>Our classes maintain a friendly and fun atmosphere and are held at the
following times:</p>

<h3>Thursdays</h3>

<dl>
<dt>7.30-8.30pm Freestyle dance class</dt>

<dl>
<dt>A fast, flashy Rock'n'Roll based dance set to modern dance music (nightclub
style).</dt>
</dl>

<dt>8.30-9.30pm Latin class</dt>

<dd>Merengue and Salsa, danced to hypnotic rhythms from the Caribbean.</dd>

<dd>Classes will be held in the University of Canterbury Student's Association
Ballroom, 90 Ilam Rd.</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Class Format and Charges</h2>

<p>Generally there is instruction for 45 minutes followed by 15 minutes
of free dancing. The style of the class depends on the individual teacher
but mostly the students are arranged in a circle with the teacher at the
centre. Partners change every few minutes with the male moving on to the
next partner in the circle.</p>

<p>Each nights attendance costs $3 for students and $5 for non-students.
You can attend as many classes as you like on a night without having to
pay twice. Club social events, trips, and parties are open to anyone. </p>

<p>
<br><font SIZE=+1>You are <blink>WELCOME</blink> to come along and check
us out any time.</font> 
<br>
<br>Click <a href="http://www.mech.canterbury.ac.nz/clubs/latindnc/limages.htm">here</a>
to see images from our past and present, friends, good times... 
<br>Click <a href="http://www.mech.canterbury.ac.nz/clubs/latindnc/l_event.htm">here</a>
to find out about our 1996 and 1997 events. 
<br>Click <a href="http://www.nzdances.co.nz/dance/general/general.htm">here</a>
to be whipped through cyberspace to New Zealand Dances.</p>

<p>To find out more about the club you can mail me at <a href="mailto:lintotab@cad.canterbury.ac.nz">lintotab@cad.canterbury.ac.nz</a>
</p>

</body>
