<H2>WELCOME TO THE GREENPEACE INTERNATIONAL HOMEPAGE</h2></center>
<APPLET height=1 width=1>

<font size="-1">Use the navigator bar at the top of this page & click on the icons (or use the text links above) to visit our main pages.  Visit the <a href="/key.html"><B>key to icons</B></a> page if you're really not sure where to find things or check out <a href="/navigate.html">
<B>how to use</B></a> the  Greenpeace Web Navigator. Our <a href="http://www.greenpeace.org/cgi-bin/fx?DB=GPALL"><img src="/icons/info.gif" width=24 height=24 border=0 
align=center alt="search"></a> Search Engine. <A HREF="gopher://Gopher.Greenpeace.org/">
<img src="/icons/gopher.gif" width=24 height=24 border=0 alt="Greenpeace Gopher site" align=center>
</a>Gopher site, and other services can be found on the <a href="/iinf.html"><img src="/icons/iinf.gif" border=0 width=24 height=24 align=center alt="information"></A> information page.  The <a href="/shot.html">
<img src="/icons/shot.gif" border=0 width=24 height=24 align=center alt="hotpage"></A> hotpage is always worth a visit.  Greenpeace nuclear campaign launch their new "no.nukes" site on 18th December and release a  <a href="/~comms/no.nukes/transhn.html"><img src="/icons/ntransh.gif" align="center"  border=0 alt="Nukes shipment" width=24 height=24></a>confidential French Government Document on Radioactive Shipment Route.
</font>

<br><br><img WIDTH=560 HEIGHT=29 src="/icons/forest.gif" 
alt="-------------------------------------------------------------"><br><br>
</applet>
Greenpeace is an independent, campaigning organisation which uses non-violent, creative confrontation to expose global environmental problems, 
and to force the solutions which are essential to a green and peaceful future..<p>
Greenpeace's goal is to ensure the ability of the earth to nurture life 
in all its diversity. Therefore Greenpeace seeks to:
<ul>
<li>Protect biodiversity in all its forms.</li>
<li>Prevent pollution and abuse of the earth's ocean, land, air and fresh water.</li>
<li>End all nuclear threats.</li>
<li>Promote peace, global disarmament and non-violence.</li>

</ul><P>
<img WIDTH=560 HEIGHT=29 src="/icons/forest.gif" 
alt="-------------------------------------------------------------"><br>
Webmaster is:
<address>webmaster@www.greenpeace.org</address>
You can <a href="mailto:webmaster@xs2.greenpeace.org">mail him</a> here.
