<li><a href="~thoml/brphoto.html">Sounds of the Brazilian rain forest</a>
<li><a href="/~comms/brent/may22d.html">Recorded account</a> of Shell's attempt on May 22nd to re-occupy the Brent Spar using the Stadive (diving platform).
</ul>



