<h2>Anti-nuclear:</h2>
<ul>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.pal.xgw.fi/hew/">Gary Au's
anti-nuclear page</A> </li>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.vicnet.net.au/~theage/french.htm"> 
