No More Hiroshimas Coalition</A> (Australia)</li>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.icepp.s.u-tokyo.ac.jp/~keshi/"> 
Stop nuclear tests!</A> Uni of Tokyo (Japan)</li>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.peg.apc.org/~freedom/">No more nuclear tests</A> 
Boycot. International Freedom (Australia)</li> 
<li> <A 
HREF="http://www.uampfa.berkeley.edu/pfa/filmseries/bdeath/bdhome.html">
Becoming Death: Cinema and the Atomic Age</a> at Pacific Film Archive at UC 
Berkeley (USA)</li>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.peacewire.org/pw">PEACEwire</a>, Public 
Education for Peace Society, Vancouver (Canada)</li>
<li> <A HREF="http://www.nucmed.buffalo.edu:8000/">Physicians for Social 
Responsibility</a>, PSR (IPPNW). (USA)</li>
<li> <a href="http://www.xs4all.nl/~foeint/murup.html">Friends of the 
Earth</a> Moruroa activities</li>
<li> <a href="http://www.xs4all.nl/~cor/gifs/chirac.gif">Chirac Rules</a> 
cartoon postcard</li>
