<TD VALIGN=TOP>
WHAT YOU CAN DO
 
<I><p>As you will see from the Greenpeace International Nuclear pages,
we are campaigning to stop reprocessing, to start the global
phase-out of nuclear power and to bring about nuclear
disarmament.
 
<p>But we need your help.  In this section we will let you know
about demonstrations and activities that you can join, advise you
on letters and faxes that we would like you to send and generally
ask for your help in the global campaign for a nuclear-free
future.</I>
 
<p>WATCH THIS SPACE FOR DETAILS!!!!!!!

