<a href="geneng.html"> <img align=left border=0 width=60 height=60 src="../icons/biogen.gif"> <B>Genetic Engineering</B></a><font size=-1> poses a serious threat to the earth's biodiversity. It allows genes to be transferred between completely unrelated species. Human genes have been moved into fish; bacterial and animal genes into plants...</font>
</td></tr></table>
