<P>If you require any of these photographs for<B> professional reproduction purposes only</B> please <a href="mailto:greenpeace.communications@green2.greenpeace.org"> E-mail the Greenpeace Picture Library</a> quoting the photo reference number, your name, e-mail address, organisation, fax number, and intended usage, stating the format you require.

<P>These photographs are taken by various photographers and are copyright protected.  They may be viewed or kept for private purposes.  Copying, distribution, commercial use, or any other use other than for personal purposes without prior written permission is prohibited.  Any violation will be subject to legal action.
<P>These GIFs are between 50K (landscape) and 90K (portrait).  Dimensions are 6" wide and 72 dpi.))

<br>These JPEGS are between 25K (landscape) and 40K (portrait).  Dimensions are 6" wide and 72 dpi.))

