http://greenpeace.meer.net:80/~comms/rw/jul09d.html 204.188.97.9 19970121062523 text/html 14824
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 06:25:21 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
