<P>
<H1>FRANCE HALTS NUCLEAR TESTING</H1>

<H1>Greenpeace continues international campaign against nuclear tests and for a comprehensive test ban treaty</H1>
</center>
<p><a href="mar20.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0></a>
<font size=>RAINBOW WARRIOR FREED AFTER FIVE MONTHS OF FRENCH MILITARY DETENTION-</font><a href="mar20.html">Press release</a> and <a href="mar20d.html">pictures</a> 
<BR><BR><BR>
<p><a href="jan29.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0></a>INTERNATIONAL PROTEST FORCES FRENCH TO REDUCE TEST PROGRAMME? <a href="jan29.html">Greenpeace welcomes Chirac announcement</a> of halt to testing.-<a href="thanks
.html">THANKS to all who joined the worldwide protest</a>.

<p><a href="jan22.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0></a>CTBT NEGOTIATIONS OPEN 22nd JANUARY;<a href="jan22.html">Account of Demonstration</a> <a href="open.html"> GREENPEACE SAYS</a>... the world wants a nuclear test b
an in 1996. (see also -<a href="pr.html#january"> press releases</A>) <BR><BR><BR> 
<p><a href="../review/95.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0>GREENPEACE'S SUCCESSES IN 1995.</a> <BR><BR><BR> 
<p><a href="dec27.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0>FRANCE DETONATES FIFTH NUCLEAR TEST</a><A HREF="sep10d.html #bomvid">Video clip of first test...</a> 8 seconds of video with sound (1.4MB.) <BR><BR><BR>  

<p><a href="pr.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0>PRESS RELEASES FROM THE RAINBOW WARRIOR CAMPAIGN</a> Latest campaign news, developments and contacts.<BR><BR><BR> 

<p><a href="diary.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0>BULLETINS FROM ABOARD THE RAINBOW WARRIOR AND MANUTEA: </a>Chronology and reports on actions from the crew and campaigners with pictures and video clips.<BR><BR>

<p><a href="chin.html"><image align=left src="rwlogo02.gif" width=36 height=36 border=0>GREENPEACE CAMPAIGNS AGAINST CHINA'S NUCLEAR TESTS</a><BR><BR><BR> 

