<H2>Welcome at the Greenpeace International WAIS search page</H2>
<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="/cgi-bin/wwwwais">
<IMG SRC="/pics/wwwwais.gif" ALT="[WAIS Search]">
This is a searchable index of information collected by Greenpeace 
International, which is campaign data stored in the <a 
href="gopher://gopher.greenpeace.org/11/campaign/">gopher</a> and 
<a href="ftp://ftp.greenpeace.org/pub/campaigns/cdromgp/">ftp</a> 
directories, plus the gopher archives of the regular <a 
href="gopher://gopher.greenpeace.org/11/press/">press releases</a>. 
<p>
<B>Note:</B>
<I>This service can only be used from a forms-capable browser.</I><br>
If you have no such browser, you can search the same data with the search option 
in the <a href="gopher://gopher.greenpeace.org/7/campaign/campaigns">gopher.</a>
<P>
