ard.  This debate area is moderated so your contributions will not appear immediately.<br></td></tr></table><!--PRESS TABLE--><a name="press"></a><table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=576><tr><tH colspan=2 valign=center><a href="#idc home"><img src="../icons/bpress.gif" width=576 height=72 border=0 align=center></a></td></tr>

