<HEAD><H4>Brent Spar Abandonment
Impact Hypothesis

December 1994</H4>






<P>Prepared for Shell U.K. Exploration and Production
by Rudall Blanchard Associates Limited

<LI>Brent Spar Abandonment - Impact Hypothesis 15/12/94</HEAD><BODY>

<P><H4>CONTENTS</H4>



	<P><H4><A HREF="#SYNOPSIS">1 .SYNOPSIS </A></H4>

	<P><H4><A HREF="#STRUCTURE">2.STRUCTURE OF DOCUMENT </A></H4>	 
	<P><H4><A HREF="#SUMMARY">3.SUMMARY INFORMATION ON THE BRENT SPAR </A><H4>
