	<li>	7.5. Environmental Impacts of Hydrocarbon and Heavy Metal Releases 	22

	<P><A HREF="#SCALE">8. 	FATE AND EFFECTS OF LOW SPECIFIC ACTIVITY SCALE </A></H4>
	<li>8.1. 	Approach to Assessment of Radiological Impact 		24
